Ranger Help for: essence of the land
======================================

SYNTAX:      essence
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,road,beach,
             mountain,arctic,barren,outside
SLOT COST:   7
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  religious

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to draw power from the surrounding terrain,
granting temporary stat buffs that vary depending on the type of land.
A forest might grant agility, while mountains might grant endurance.
The strength and duration of the buffs depend on the Ranger's wisdom,
guild level, and familiarity with the terrain. This skill works best
in the Ranger's primary terrain and cannot be used in cities or
indoor areas.
